cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the application of self-attention architectures, specifically the transformer, to reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as they are also relevant to natural language processing. The paper also involves robotics and control, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics and Automation), and neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
